content: iPhoto is a photo editor and organizer application developed by Apple. iPhoto '11 is included in the iLife package along with iMovie '11 and GarageBand '11. Some features include red-eye correction, photo enhancement, and photo retouch.
NOTE: iPhoto was discontinued and replaced by Photos in 2015.

description: Printing file created by iPhoto, a photo editing application; created when an image is selected to be printed; contains data referenced for printing purposes.
